This plugin orchestrates the download of third-party recompilation and
native-port projects. None of them are bundled in this repository or its
release artifacts.

## Recompilation / native-port projects (downloaded at user request)

The catalog in `games.json` references community recompilation and
decompilation projects — e.g. Zelda 64: Recompiled
(https://github.com/Zelda64Recomp/Zelda64Recomp), Banjo: Recompiled, and
others. At the user's request, this plugin downloads each project's
prebuilt release (or build inputs) directly from that project's official
GitHub Releases. **No project binaries are redistributed by this
repository.** Each downloaded project is governed by its own upstream
license on the user's machine.

Recompiled and decompiled ports require the user to supply their own
legally-obtained game files; no copyrighted game data is included,
referenced by content, or distributed here. This plugin's own source is
BSD-3-Clause.
